title: Yung Filly's Celeb Lock-In
overview: Yung Filly's Celeb Lock-In sees viral comedy star Yung Filly inviting four households from across the UK to take part in a one-of-a-kind showdown, with help from Filly's celebrity guests.Expect rap freestyles, celeb prank phone-calls and exclusive house tours, bad dancing, and lots and lots of chaos - nothing is off limits for Filly and his celeb guests.
